    "description": "在这个超级紧张的平台游戏中，进入一个秘密堡垒，取回一个被盗的能量球，有150多个具有挑战性的手工制作的屏幕。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/391be050ff919bd6ad64dd933dde4395.webp?t=1763834448\" width=223 height=36 /></span><br><br>这款游戏的特点是有很多具有不同能力的敌人，如射出激光、制导导弹和分部爆炸，在死亡时产生爆炸或具有能量场。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/1a0369b215961ca23bc41ff168214a20.poster.avif?t=1763834448\" width=434 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/1a0369b215961ca23bc41ff168214a20.webm?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/1a0369b215961ca23bc41ff168214a20.mp4?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/findKeysTCh.png?t=1763834448\" /></span><br><br>发现一个与周围地形不匹配的地形区？射杀它吧! 它可能隐藏着一把钥匙（本游戏中的一种可收集物品）。有些钥匙在明显的位置，但很难拿到。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/05fac5eb79ae0b44922737425fac4d6a.poster.avif?t=1763834448\" width=360 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/05fac5eb79ae0b44922737425fac4d6a.webm?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/05fac5eb79ae0b44922737425fac4d6a.mp4?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/a95ff3fa792c8ebea5097f9e384ca2b0.webp?t=1763834448\" width=260 height=36 /></span><br><br>愉快的游戏危险，如由灯光触发激活的敌人产卵门户，燃烧的落块，移动的平台，传送带，激光或定时消失的块。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/cc6a6d7a1bce12594ad5b8d29c7f43bd.poster.avif?t=1763834448\" width=510 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/cc6a6d7a1bce12594ad5b8d29c7f43bd.webm?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/cc6a6d7a1bce12594ad5b8d29c7f43bd.mp4?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/9d611e7425cdec68afa04d767445f45d.webp?t=1763834448\" width=185 height=36 /></span><br><br>快速的死亡和闪电般的重生。要克服这个游戏的困难挑战，就需要这些。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/179818329bbc1fcddcc40761c103b879.poster.avif?t=1763834448\" width=310 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/179818329bbc1fcddcc40761c103b879.webm?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/179818329bbc1fcddcc40761c103b879.mp4?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/92b623e50e0bfedfab8ee4c9bace92c9.webp?t=1763834448\" width=147 height=36 /></span><br><br>控制方式流畅、精确、简单、易记：冲刺、射击、跑步和跳跃。由于精确的控制，可以准确地将角色放在你想要的地方。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/4a6f9d3f3d0aeddcf8c9bd32486332c1.webp?t=1763834448\" width=147 height=36 /></span><br><br>摧毁强大而富有挑战性的老板。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/e4d868d899ca24443099c7be7158911e.avif?t=1763834448\" width=614 height=424 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/cef483fdc35baacf4e501221430dc568.poster.avif?t=1763834448\" width=480 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/cef483fdc35baacf4e501221430dc568.webm?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128730/extras/cef483fdc35baacf4e501221430dc568.mp4?t=1763834448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>",
